+ * enum adau1961_micbias_voltage - Microphone bias voltage
+ * @ADAU1961_MICBIAS_0_90_AVDD: 0.9 * AVDD
+ * @ADAU1961_MICBIAS_0_65_AVDD: 0.65 * AVDD
